revision.text:
'''Bhul''' is a community that resides in the hilly region of [[Nepal]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Nepal Census 2011 |url=https://unstats.un.org/unsD/demographic/sources/census/wphc/Nepal/Nepal-Census-2011-Vol1.pdf |website=Nepal Census |publisher=Nepal Census |accessdate=10 August 2018}}</ref> Bhul is one of the four castes in its region ([[Rosyara]], Paneru, and Damai being the others).

